---
---
<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-content">
        <div class="tag">Why We Are Different</div>
        <h2 class="about-title">Say Goodbye to <span class="text-gradient">Slow, Vulnerable</span> Sites</h2>
        <p class="about-desc">
          Most agencies build websites using outdated, bloated platforms (like WordPress) that require constant security updates, database management, and heavy servers. This results in slow load times and vulnerable sites.
        </p>
        <p class="about-desc">
          We do things differently. By implementing a <strong>Headless Architecture</strong>, we separate your frontend from the backend. Your site compiles to pre-rendered HTML/CSS served instantly via global networks (CDNs).
        </p>
        
        <div class="metrics">
          <div class="metric">
            <span class="metric-num">100%</span>
            <span class="metric-label">Pre-rendered HTML</span>
          </div>
          <div class="metric">
            <span class="metric-num">&lt;0.5s</span>
            <span class="metric-label">Average Load Time</span>
          </div>
          <div class="metric">
            <span class="metric-num">Zero</span>
            <span class="metric-label">Database Risks</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="about-comparison glass-panel">
        <h3 class="comp-title">The Architechture Comparison</h3>
        
        <div class="comp-item">
          <div class="comp-header">
            <span class="comp-label">Legacy WordPress approach</span>
            <span class="comp-val val-bad">Slow & Heavy</span>
          </div>
          <div class="comp-bar-container">
            <div class="comp-bar bar-legacy" style="width: 85%"></div>
          </div>
          <p class="comp-details">Every visitor triggers PHP compiling & database queries. Bloated plugins load unused code.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="comp-item">
          <div class="comp-header">
            <span class="comp-label">Eastern Wave Headless approach</span>
            <span class="comp-val val-good">Instant</span>
          </div>
          <div class="comp-bar-container">
            <div class="comp-bar bar-headless" style="width: 15%"></div>
          </div>
          <p class="comp-details">Static pre-compiled files serve immediately from edge CDNs. Pure HTML/CSS with zero-bloat JS.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: 120px 24px;
    background: rgba(12, 13, 20, 0.4);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .tag {
    color: var(--accent-cyan);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .about-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .about-desc {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .metrics {
    display: flex;
    gap: 32px;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }

  .metric {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .metric-num {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .metric-label {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  /* Comparison Panel Styling */
  .about-comparison {
    padding: 40px;
  }

  .comp-title {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .comp-item {
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .comp-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .comp-label {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .comp-val {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .val-bad {
    color: #ef4444;
  }

  .val-good {
    color: var(--accent-cyan);
  }

  .comp-bar-container {
    height: 6px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    border-radius: 3px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .comp-bar {
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 3px;
  }

  .bar-legacy {
    background: #ef4444;
  }

  .bar-headless {
    background: var(--accent-wave);
  }

  .comp-details {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 991px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }
  }
</style>
